OL,5, The inquest into the death of a head   
OL,6, teacher who killed herself has heard   
OL,7, how she looked in "physical pain" after
OL,8, a school Ofsted inspection.            
OL,10,FAs it became clearer the school may be 
OL,11,Fdowngraded, lead inspector Alan Derry  
OL,12,Fsaid, Ruth Perry "was very upset, very 
OL,13,Ftearful", saying "she couldn't show her
OL,14,Fface again".                           
OL,16,FMrs Perry was head teacher at Caversham
OL,17,FPrimary School for 13 years.           
OL,19,FHer death led to a debate about how    
OL,20,FOfsted inspections in England worked.  
